data.description: Welcome to your serene countryside retreat! Nestled on 2.5 sprawling acres of lush greenery, this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom single-family home offers a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. Upon entering, you're greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors. Large living area and formal dining room offers an inviting space to host memorable dinner parties and family gatherings. Step outside to discover your own private oasis, where endless possibilities await on 2.5 acres of land. Whether you dream of cultivating a bountiful garden, raising animals, or simply soaking in the natural beauty of your surroundings, this expansive property is ready for your rural lifestyle aspirations.  Additional features of this property include a well system and a septic system. With its idyllic location in a rural/country area, you'll enjoy the serenity of country living while still being within easy reach of local amenities and attractions. Make your appointment today!
